OL,5, Energy suppliers have been failing     
OL,6, vulnerable customers, the sector's     
OL,7, watchdog has said, as they face a      
OL,8, costly and cold winter.                
OL,10,FRegulator Ofgem has ordered            
OL,11,Fimprovements after it found problems at
OL,12,Fall 17 firms as part of a review.      
OL,14,FAmong its findings were examples of    
OL,15,Ffirms setting debt repayments so high  
OL,16,Fthat customers decided not to top-up   
OL,17,Ftheir pre-payment meters.              
OL,19,FBut some of the suppliers named hit    
OL,20,Fback at Ofgem's "incomplete" review.   
